### Import Payload Field Type in TypeScript

Source: https://github.com/payloadcms/payload/blob/main/docs/fields/overview.mdx

Import the `Field` type and other common types from the `payload` package to enhance type safety when defining fields in Payload CMS configurations.

```ts
import type { Field } from 'payload'
```

--------------------------------

### Configure Field Type in Payload CMS (TypeScript)

Source: https://github.com/payloadcms/payload/blob/main/docs/fields/overview.mdx

This TypeScript example shows how to set the 'type' property for a field in Payload CMS. The 'type' property determines the field's behavior and appearance within the Admin Panel, matching it to a defined Field Type.

```typescript
import type { Field } from 'payload'

export const MyField: Field = {
  type: 'text',
  name: 'myField'
}
```

