### Import Client Field Component Types in Payload CMS (TSX)

Source: https://github.com/payloadcms/payload/blob/main/docs/fields/overview.mdx

This code snippet demonstrates how to import various client and server component types for custom fields in Payload CMS. These types, such as `TextFieldClientComponent` and `TextFieldServerComponent`, ensure type safety when building custom field components for different field types and environments.

```tsx
import type {
  TextFieldClientComponent,
  TextFieldServerComponent,
  TextFieldClientProps,
  TextFieldServerProps,
  // ...and so on for each Field Type
} from 'payload'
```

