### Define Payload CMS Radio Field

Source: https://github.com/payloadcms/payload/blob/main/tools/claude-plugin/skills/payload/reference/FIELDS.md

Defines a radio field named 'priority' with 'low', 'medium', 'high' options and a default 'medium' value. The admin layout is set to horizontal. This is a basic field type for single selection in Payload CMS.

```ts
import type { RadioField } from 'payload'

const radioField: RadioField = {
  name: 'priority',
  type: 'radio',
  options: [
    { label: 'Low', value: 'low' },
    { label: 'Medium', value: 'medium' },
    { label: 'High', value: 'high' },
  ],
  defaultValue: 'medium',
  admin: {
    layout: 'horizontal', // or 'vertical'
  },
}
```

