### Integrate Custom React UI Components in Payload CMS

Source: https://github.com/payloadcms/payload/blob/main/tools/claude-plugin/skills/payload/reference/FIELDS.md

Demonstrates how to define a 'ui' field for embedding custom React components into the Payload CMS admin. This field type does not store data but allows for highly customized UI elements for Field and Cell views.

```ts
import type { UIField } from 'payload'

const uiField: UIField = {
  name: 'customMessage',
  type: 'ui',
  admin: {
    components: {
      Field: '/path/to/CustomFieldComponent',
      Cell: '/path/to/CustomCellComponent', // For list view
    },
  },
}
```

