### Configure Form Builder Fields

Source: https://github.com/payloadcms/payload/blob/main/docs/plugins/form-builder.mdx

Customize the available field types for form editors within the Form Builder plugin by configuring the `fields` option. You can enable fields with `true`, disable them with `false`, or provide partial Block configurations for advanced customization.

```typescript
// payload.config.ts
formBuilderPlugin({
  // ...
  fields: {
    text: true,
    textarea: true,
    select: true,
    radio: true,
    email: true,
    state: true,
    country: true,
    checkbox: true,
    number: true,
    message: true,
    date: false,
    payment: false,
  },
})
```

