### Set up Upload Field in Payload CMS

Source: https://github.com/payloadcms/payload/blob/main/tools/claude-plugin/skills/payload/reference/FIELDS.md

Configures an 'upload' field in Payload CMS, typically used for linking to media assets. It specifies the 'relationTo' collection (e.g., 'media') and can enforce required status. The 'filterOptions' allow for MIME type filtering, ensuring only specific file types can be uploaded.

```typescript
import type { UploadField } from 'payload'

const uploadField: UploadField = {
  name: 'featuredImage',
  type: 'upload',
  relationTo: 'media',
  required: true,
  filterOptions: {
    mimeType: { contains: 'image' },
  },
}
```

