### Rename Payload CMS 'Fields' Type to 'FormState'

Source: https://github.com/payloadcms/payload/blob/main/docs/migration-guide/overview.mdx

The `Fields` type in Payload CMS has been renamed to `FormState` for improved semantic clarity. Developers should update their import statements to reflect this change.

```diff
- import type { Fields } from 'payload'
+ import type { FormState } from 'payload'
```

