### Create Payload CMS Horizontal Row Layout

Source: https://github.com/payloadcms/payload/blob/main/tools/claude-plugin/skills/payload/reference/FIELDS.md

Illustrates how to use a 'row' field to arrange other fields horizontally within the Payload CMS admin panel. It groups 'firstName' and 'lastName' text fields, each taking 50% width, for presentational purposes only.

```ts
import type { RowField } from 'payload'

const rowField: RowField = {
  type: 'row',
  fields: [
    {
      name: 'firstName',
      type: 'text',
      admin: { width: '50%' },
    },
    {
      name: 'lastName',
      type: 'text',
      admin: { width: '50%' },
    },
  ],
}
```
